rows.name: Don't cause any trouble.
Well, I'm off.
Come home soon, okay?
Go and report to the captain.
Understood.
Ugh, another rough day...
Fancy a drink on the way home?
I'm as hungry as a Volff, mo...
Welcome home!
It's good to be back!
I know a really nice place.
Want to go together?
Okay! Same place tomorrow!

Shouldn't you be tending
to the shop out front?

I haven't been feeling so well lately,
so my son's been handling things...
Oh, what a bother!
Urk...

Instead of hanging around here,
shouldn't you go to a medical facility?
Daddy, are you going to the war too?
Do you have to?

Daddypon!
Mamapon!
Where are you, mo?
Now that's a big castle...

There's nothing like that in Gula,
that's for sure.
Where have the children run off to, mo?
Just focus on the job, all right?
We've got to fix this before nightfall.
It'll be a disaster if someone falls.

My friend went to Gula.
I wonder if they're all right...
Mama, can I have a sweet?

Oh, all right then.
But just one!
I feel for the soldiers...
What's up with that guy?
He drank too much. It's the usual story.
I could really go for an open-air bath...

The air here is more biting
than I thought, mo!
Where did I put it...?
I can't get in without the key!

This open-air hot spring is the best in
the Empire.

I could come here every day and
never get tired of it.

That big Divine Beast weapon is
gone now, huh?
Maybe it went back to the palace?

Hurry, mo!
Someone's coming, mo!!

Quiet!
Just a little longer.
Where should we go today?
I want to look at board games!
Got anything new?

As a matter of fact, I got a new shipment
in just yesterday.
How does it taste?
Yes! It's delicious, mo!

Do you have any books
on military tactics?
Allow me to take a look...

When I grow up,
I want to be a salvager!
I want to be a soldier, mo!
Over here this time, huh...?
Let's just get this over with.
Hm, what should I make today...
I recommend these vegetables.

Granny, come on!
Hurry up!

I'm coming,
I'm coming.

Wow! Whoa!
Superbia is AWESOME.

I can't believe how
bright it is at night!
Come on, Aniki! Save some for me!
No way! It's all mine!
That's not right!

Waaah!
I'm sorry...
Does this bring back memories?

It reminds me of my days
in the army band...

Even the posts on the notice board
have gotten grim lately...
They're so lucky...
The security here's impressive!

It's the heart of the Empire, mo!
Of course it is, mo!
Dammit... Drank too much...

That's what you get for not knowing
your limits...

Today we'll be patrolling around
the research labs!
Sir! Yes, sir!

So many bathhouses!
Which one should I go to today?
It's so bright, mo!
Are you sure it won't explode, mo?
A lot of cargo to move today?
Yep, another tough one...
...I'm completely lost.
Late on my first day?! Unbelievable.
This door doesn't open, mo?
Yeah, I've rarely seen it open...
Here, let me help.
Thank you!
What kind of place is Avaritia?

It's a very bustling place, mo!
You should go and see for yourself, mo!
Still working at this hour?
Yeah, it's taking a while...
How are you doing over there?
Nearly done!

Just what you'd expect
from a military facility, mo.

Let's head back before
anyone shows up.

What is this graffiti...?
Some kind of new code?
Want to go shopping together?
I suppose so...
Ooh, aren't you a strapping young man!

Why don't you come have
a bite to eat at my place?

I'm sorry.
I tried my best, but...

The older kids get to play
out in the open. It's not fair!

Hey, that's dangerous!
Come back here!

Look, Dad! There's some kind
of entrance down below!

I've been seeing a lot more Drivers
around the palace recently.

I hear they've been
recruiting from all over.

I can't hear you, maggots!
Sound off like you mean it!

Sir!
Yes, sir!

Sir!
Yes, sir!

Sir!
Yes, sir!

Sir!
Yes, sir!

Tomorrow's training will be even harder!
Aren't you all thrilled?!

Sir!
Yes, sir!!!

Sir!
Yes, sir!!!

Sir!
Yes, sir!!!

Sir!
Yes, sir!!!

Sir!
Yes, sir!!!
Ugh, I give up...
One! Two! Three!

Anyone who fails this exercise gets
a one-way ticket to Gula!
How many ships today...?
I hear they're researching a new model.
Does it look fixable?
This part keeps breaking, doesn't it...

I hear we have enemies
within our own borders now.
No rest for the wicked, I suppose.

Be ready for battle.
Make sure you know how to use this.
I will.
Let's play ball!

Yeah!
And after that, we can play soldiers!

What should I do...? I think I dropped the
key somewhere around here...

It's the key to the harbor gate...
My CO is going to kill me!

I can't believe it... Did I really
drop it off the bridge...?

Fabelle is never going to let me hear
the end of this... Ugh... I'll have to
keep looking tomorrow.
That's a huge vehicle!

The Divine Beast battleships that came to
Gula were even bigger, you know...
I'll get this cargo to the city, double-time, mo!
This crate is so heavy, mo...
That's quite a load of cargo you've got.

There's nothing shady here, mo!
Check it all you want, mo!!
It's much brighter than a torch, isn't it?
The city itself is even brighter.
It's so dusty here, mo!

Sand in my mouth, mo!
Ptooey! Ptooey!

Please use the far lift
for transporting Armu.
Why? Is this one off-limits?

Be careful when you're
operating this machinery.

Are you sure you haven't
forgotten any cargo?
Be on your best behavior.
It's not my first guard shift, you know...

Doing maintenance on this geothermal
plant is life-threatening work.

I've asked them time and again, but the
army can't seem to fix our monster problem...

We use the gondola to get around here.
Too many monsters on the ground...

So...hot... It's like Superbia's
Divine Beast is running a fever!

If you fell in there... Well, let's just
say you don't want to fall in there.

I'm actually afraid of heights...
I don't know why they stationed me up here...
Let's just watch out for each other, okay?

The industrial lift is on the left.
The passenger elevator is a bit further in.
Let's hurry to Alba Margen, mo!
Let's go, mo!

Well, well...
Did you get in through that little gap?
Don't fall out of the elevator.
I want to go hoooome!

...There are procedures for
that sort of thing.
Where has everyone gone...?
Aren't you hungry?
...I'll be fine...
